{"ID":"20240924142912-7vwy10z","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20240924142912-7vwy10z","title":"机器学习问题","type":"doc","updated":"20250211091410"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240924142912-8izro7v","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20240924142912-8izro7v","updated":"20240924152753"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"准确率、精确率、召回率和F1分数"}]},{"ID":"20240924143018-x35da2p","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240924143018-x35da2p","updated":"20240924152753"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"准确率 (Accuracy)"}]},{"ID":"20240924143732-a8oel7d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240924143732-a8oel7d","updated":"20240924143732"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"表示正确分类的样本占总样本的比例。计算公式为："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\text{Accuracy} = \\frac{\\text{TP} + \\text{TN}}{\\text{TP} + \\text{TN} + \\text{FP} + \\text{FN}}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，其中TP是真阳性，TN是真阴性，FP是假阳性，FN是假阴性。"}]},{"ID":"20240924143842-631vxfs","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240924143842-631vxfs","updated":"20240924152753"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240924143842-octerrc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240924143842-octerrc","updated":"20240924152753"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"真阳性（TP）：实际患有癌症，且测试结果显示阳性的患者数量\n真阴性（TN）：实际未患癌症，且测试结果显示阴性的患者数量\n假阳性（FP）：实际未患癌症，但测试结果显示阳性的患者数量（误诊）\n假阴性（FN）：实际患有癌症，但测试结果显示阴性的患者数量（漏诊）"}]}]},{"ID":"20240924143721-ek9p789","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240924143721-ek9p789","updated":"20240924143750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"精确率 (Precision)"}]},{"ID":"20240924143751-j0das3m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240924143751-j0das3m","updated":"20240924143751"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"表示预测为正样本的样本中，实际为正样本的比例。计算公式为："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\text{Precision} = \\frac{\\text{TP}}{\\text{TP} + \\text{FP}}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。精确率高说明假阳性少。"}]},{"ID":"20240924143721-7t86oaj","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240924143721-7t86oaj","updated":"20240924143753"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"召回率 (Recall)"}]},{"ID":"20240924143753-c3m7oyr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240924143753-c3m7oyr","updated":"20240924143753"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"表示实际为正样本的样本中，被正确预测为正样本的比例。计算公式为："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\text{Recall} = \\frac{\\text{TP}}{\\text{TP} + \\text{FN}}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。召回率高说明假阴性少。"}]},{"ID":"20240924143721-nsoldhk","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240924143721-nsoldhk","updated":"20240930142042"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"F1分数 (F1 Score)"}]},{"ID":"20240924143756-mpoykaz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240924143756-mpoykaz","updated":"20240924143756"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是精确率和召回率的调和平均数，用于综合评估模型性能。计算公式为："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"F1 = 2 \\times \\frac{\\text{Precision} \\times \\text{Recall}}{\\text{Precision} + \\text{Recall}}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。F1分数越高，模型综合表现越好。"}]},{"ID":"20240924143239-oefloxr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240924143239-oefloxr","updated":"20240924143239"}},{"ID":"20241029100746-5m5bq15","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20241029100746-5m5bq15","updated":"20241203142754"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"旋转目标检测"}]},{"ID":"20240930141724-zpgws97","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20240930141724-zpgws97","updated":"20241203142806"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"卷积"}]},{"ID":"20241111094405-im8xukm","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20241111094405-im8xukm","updated":"20241203142806"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20241203142806-dwbi89d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241203142806-dwbi89d","updated":"20241203142806"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"用过原生ps功能的基本上都能理解。一个图片在ps中的处理过程无非就是。处理一个个的像素点。一个彩色照片就是三张rgb照片叠到一起组成的。现在有一张生活照要把它ps成蓝底的证件照。这时候可以把照片放的无限大，就会发现照片是有无数个小像素点组成。在纯手工的情况下，把背景的像素点一个一个改成蓝色。但是你会发现像素点一个一个改就很麻烦。特别是遇到颜色相近的位置，肯定有大片去改的想法。有想法就要实践，其实这个过程就是把1✖️1的卷积核变成了类似与4✖️4的卷积核，一次改的面积就大了。就这种把大批量颜色全改成纯色像素点的情况下，对图片还是很友好的。但是遇到人头像边缘和改蓝色这个区域的边界就很麻烦。就是所谓的卷积核太大了，就可能把头发丝也改成蓝色背景了。显示不行，所以把卷积核卷小一点，这样子就清楚的分辨出来头发丝和蓝色底图了类似与ps的笔刷的粗细。只不过现在所谓的卷积是计算机操作的。它只认识1和0，"}]},{"ID":"20241203142806-8qqdrj9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241203142806-8qqdrj9","updated":"20241203142806"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，它也是处理一个像素点的数据，只不过这个像素点是个转化后的二进制，图片就是好几个图层的大矩阵"}]},{"ID":"20241203142806-eil3dc1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241203142806-eil3dc1","updated":"20241203142806"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，想要批量对大矩阵操作，自然最好的办法就是对矩阵进行加减乘除。"}]},{"ID":"20241203142806-fguhssa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241203142806-fguhssa","updated":"20241203142806"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"你自己找个合适的卷积核也就是相对来说大小合适的小矩阵去和这个大矩阵做运算。类比到刚才图片像素点上，假如图片这块区域是一大片蓝色天空，我们就可以搞个大点的卷积核，它对这块区域做的运算肯定基本都是一致的。这样运算速度也很快。搞个小的卷积核，在遇到头发丝和蓝色背景这块，它就能很清楚的通过计算数值反应出来两个区域的不同。自然我们也就标记出来了(识别出来了）。"}]},{"ID":"20241203142806-okj45cz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241203142806-okj45cz","updated":"20241203142806"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"基本上这个原理的细节都是这个实例的不同情况。像什么池化了 ，等等"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111094405-j2j4ab7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111094405-j2j4ab7","updated":"20241111094405"}},{"ID":"20241111094405-qsu57dx","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20241111094405-qsu57dx","updated":"20241111100757"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"NPU问题"}]},{"ID":"20241111094411-acjp6k8","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20241111094411-acjp6k8","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20241111094421-6f7ip8d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-6f7ip8d","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在卷积神经网络（CNN）中，矩阵运算是最核心的计算任务之一，尤其是在卷积层的运算过程中。NPU（神经网络处理单元）通过以下几种方式对矩阵运算进行优化，从而大大提高计算效率，尤其在图像处理和目标检测等任务中表现出显著优势。"}]},{"ID":"20241111094421-m3ololk","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-m3ololk","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1. **并行计算优化**"}]},{"ID":"20241111094421-buacjmx","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-buacjmx","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111094421-3dhsnh0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-3dhsnh0","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111094421-wqfbldd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-wqfbldd","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**数据并行性**：卷积操作的计算涉及大量的矩阵乘法，NPU通过并行化这些运算来显著提高性能。例如，对于每个卷积核的计算，NPU可以将输入图像的不同部分分配到多个计算单元（如矩阵乘法单元、加法单元）上同时处理，利用硬件并行能力加速卷积计算。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111094421-klpyw0c","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-klpyw0c","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111094421-39o235m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-39o235m","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**深度并行性**：卷积层中通常有多个卷积核，每个卷积核会处理图像的不同区域，NPU可以将多个卷积核的运算同时进行，并在硬件层面加速每个核的计算，从而加速整体计算过程。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241111094421-zguoiri","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-zguoiri","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2. **卷积操作的高效实现**"}]},{"ID":"20241111094421-ogk9a6f","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-ogk9a6f","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111094421-x8l8y9g","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-x8l8y9g","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111094421-lwjoy6z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-lwjoy6z","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**Winograd算法**：Winograd算法是一种高效的卷积计算算法，可以减少卷积操作中的乘法次数。通过使用这种算法，NPU可以将标准卷积的运算复杂度降低，从而加速卷积计算。Winograd算法适用于固定大小的卷积核，特别是在小卷积核（如3x3卷积）时效果显著。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111094421-lxoyze7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-lxoyze7","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111094421-71b6pje","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-71b6pje","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**分块和矩阵乘法优化**：卷积计算本质上可以转化为矩阵乘法，因此NPU针对卷积计算进行了矩阵乘法优化。通过将输入图像数据和卷积核数据分块，NPU可以充分利用矩阵乘法的硬件单元进行高效计算。例如，使用 **Gemmini**（一种矩阵乘法加速器）或其他矩阵乘法优化技术，NPU可以大大提高卷积操作的速度。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241111094421-26x7iut","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-26x7iut","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3. **数据重用和缓存优化**"}]},{"ID":"20241111094421-1s9aaug","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-1s9aaug","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111094421-2rml1ko","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-2rml1ko","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111094421-zbnvazk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-zbnvazk","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**数据流优化**：卷积运算需要多次访问输入数据和卷积核，NPU通过优化数据流和缓存管理来减少不必要的数据传输和冗余计算。例如，NPU可能会将输入图像分块存储在高速缓存中，减少从内存读取数据的次数，避免不必要的数据传输延迟。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111094421-zu8w6gh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-zu8w6gh","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111094421-61znt14","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-61znt14","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**局部性优化**：卷积操作通常存在数据局部性，例如卷积核与输入数据块的局部区域之间的运算。NPU可以利用这一局部性，在硬件层面进行缓存优化，减少访问主内存的延迟，提高数据重用率。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241111094421-4kabhae","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-4kabhae","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4. **量化和低精度计算**"}]},{"ID":"20241111094421-kyux9xx","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-kyux9xx","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111094421-5e2dqs9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-5e2dqs9","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111094421-tzdezup","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-tzdezup","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**低精度计算**：传统的CNN通常使用32位浮动精度（FP32）进行运算，但在NPU中，尤其是在推理阶段，采用低精度（如8位整数 INT8、16位浮点数 FP16）计算可以显著加速运算并减少功耗。NPU通过硬件支持低精度矩阵乘法和加法，从而在保证足够精度的情况下，提升卷积运算的速度。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111094421-zu095j7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-zu095j7","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111094421-b99kbc4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-b99kbc4","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**量化**：量化是将浮动点数的计算转换为整数运算的过程，这对于加速卷积神经网络（CNN）尤其重要。在推理阶段，NPU通常会使用量化算法，将权重和激活函数从浮点数转换为整数，从而减少计算复杂度并加速卷积操作。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241111094421-3l3p8e4","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-3l3p8e4","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5. **卷积的深度可分离卷积（Depthwise Separable Convolution）**"}]},{"ID":"20241111094421-gzmpd4q","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-gzmpd4q","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111094421-v577trx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-v577trx","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111094421-kgvi5hw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-kgvi5hw","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**深度可分离卷积**：标准卷积通常对每个输入通道和输出通道之间进行全连接的卷积运算，这种操作非常耗费计算资源。深度可分离卷积（如在MobileNet中使用的方式）将卷积操作拆分为两个步骤：首先对每个输入通道分别执行卷积（深度卷积），然后执行逐点卷积（1x1卷积）。NPU通过对这种操作的优化，减少了计算量，从而加速卷积过程，特别适用于移动设备和边缘计算场景。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241111094421-vi2upos","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-vi2upos","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"6. **硬件专用加速单元**"}]},{"ID":"20241111094421-dukfmf6","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-dukfmf6","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111094421-bcda2ac","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-bcda2ac","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111094421-24k9gdg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-24k9gdg","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**卷积加速器**：一些NPU芯片配备了专门的卷积加速器，这些加速器优化了卷积计算的所有关键环节，包括矩阵乘法、数据加载、卷积核的应用等。例如，华为Ascend NPU和Google的TPU都配备了高效的卷积加速单元，可以直接执行卷积运算，无需依赖通用处理器进行逐步计算。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111094421-3uwi4ch","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-3uwi4ch","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111094421-x1db2nl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-x1db2nl","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**SIMD（单指令多数据）**：许多NPU通过SIMD（单指令多数据）架构来执行并行操作，特别是在矩阵乘法中。SIMD使得NPU能够同时执行多个相同的操作，例如同时处理多个卷积核的计算。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241111094421-jw9kwdk","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-jw9kwdk","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"7. **优化的内存访问**"}]},{"ID":"20241111094421-sb7doer","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-sb7doer","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111094421-twu1lpk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-twu1lpk","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111094421-9edf08h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-9edf08h","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**按需加载数据**：卷积运算中涉及大量的数据访问，NPU通过智能内存管理和缓存策略优化内存访问模式。例如，通过利用内存层次结构（如L1、L2缓存），NPU可以根据数据访问模式智能地加载和存储数据，以减少内存带宽的瓶颈。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111094421-xskk58o","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-xskk58o","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111094421-8kn2k9w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-8kn2k9w","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**带宽优化**：NPU可能在硬件层面做出优化，以更高效地使用内存带宽。这包括流水线处理、批处理和数据并行，以确保卷积操作尽可能快地完成。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241111094421-z30s122","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-z30s122","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"8. **硬件加速的内存存储优化**"}]},{"ID":"20241111094421-sjt0y1w","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-sjt0y1w","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111094421-7sk9h1e","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-7sk9h1e","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111094421-5z7wemp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111094421-5z7wemp","updated":"20241111094421"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**行列存储模式**：卷积核和输入图像数据通常以不同的存储格式存在。NPU可以优化这些存储格式（如行列存储）来确保更高效的内存访问，从而提高数据吞吐量。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241111100137-hbpz53p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111100137-hbpz53p","updated":"20241111100137"}},{"ID":"20241111100138-z70rhr1","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20241111100138-z70rhr1","updated":"20241111100139"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20241111100139-8d1a4o9","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20241111100139-8d1a4o9","updated":"20241111100139"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"6. **内存架构与数据带宽**"}]},{"ID":"20241111100139-cvhto02","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111100139-cvhto02","updated":"20241111100139"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111100139-80n3cr1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111100139-80n3cr1","updated":"20241111100139"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111100139-frcmba4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111100139-frcmba4","updated":"20241111100139"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**片上内存（On-Chip Memory）**：片上内存容量直接影响NPU在处理大模型时的效率，如果片上内存不足，大量的数据交换可能导致算力下降。理想的NPU应当有足够的片上缓存来支持中大型模型的推理。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111100139-4es5inz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111100139-4es5inz","updated":"20241111100139"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111100139-ut3u3lp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111100139-ut3u3lp","updated":"20241111100139"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**内存带宽**：内存带宽决定了NPU的数据吞吐量，高带宽可以减少瓶颈，提升NPU的实际算力利用率。对于需要处理大规模数据的模型（如图像分类、自然语言处理），高内存带宽尤为重要。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241111100230-q78zimn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111100230-q78zimn","updated":"20241111100230"}},{"ID":"20241111100230-0b7bn8t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111100230-0b7bn8t","updated":"20241111100230"}},{"ID":"20241111100231-yj4gitj","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20241111100231-yj4gitj","updated":"20241111100231"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20241111100231-xx3rjm7","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20241111100231-xx3rjm7","updated":"20241111100231"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1. **算力（计算性能）**"}]},{"ID":"20241111100231-vq0abma","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111100231-vq0abma","updated":"20241111100231"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111100231-hu37qhb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111100231-hu37qhb","updated":"20241111100231"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111100231-gcuob2l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111100231-gcuob2l","updated":"20241111100231"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**TOPS（Tera Operations Per Second）**：这是评估NPU算力的基本指标，表示每秒可以执行的万亿次操作数。TOPS越高，意味着NPU的理论最大算力越强，但实际性能还取决于任务类型和资源利用率。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111100231-fm06wku","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111100231-fm06wku","updated":"20241111100231"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111100231-ezihwup","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111100231-ezihwup","updated":"20241111100231"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**有效算力（Effective TOPS）**：评估实际应用中NPU的算力利用率，理论TOPS和有效TOPS可能有较大差异。例如，对于卷积神经网络的推理任务，实际的有效算力可能只有理论TOPS的50%-80%。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111100231-8no7txs","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111100231-8no7txs","updated":"20241111100231"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111100231-xygqhat","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111100231-xygqhat","updated":"20241111100231"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**FLOPs（浮点运算量）**：计算NPU执行深度学习模型推理所需的浮点运算量，FLOPs和TOPS结合可以反映NPU对特定AI任务的适配度。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241111100754-tiin92x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111100754-tiin92x","updated":"20241111100754"}},{"ID":"20241111100755-b22y854","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111100755-b22y854","updated":"20241111100755"}},{"ID":"20241111100755-99y5xor","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20241111100755-99y5xor","updated":"20250211091254"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"优化工具"}]},{"ID":"20241111100758-rii4nve","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20241111100758-rii4nve","updated":"20241111100810"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20241111100759-u2zbrsi","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20241111100759-u2zbrsi","updated":"20241111100810"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4. **性能分析与调试**："}]},{"ID":"20241111100759-tayemox","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111100759-tayemox","updated":"20241111100759"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"CANN工具链提供了性能分析和调试工具，帮助开发者识别性能瓶颈。这些工具可以提供详细的推理时间、内存使用、计算负载等信息，帮助开发者了解模型执行过程中的瓶颈，进而进行针对性的优化。"}]},{"ID":"20241111100759-vsbje7w","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111100759-vsbje7w","updated":"20241111100810"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111100759-00zaqg9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111100759-00zaqg9","updated":"20241111100759"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111100759-wrq616f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111100759-wrq616f","updated":"20241111100759"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**性能分析**：通过对模型推理的各个阶段（如输入数据预处理、模型加载、推理计算等）进行分析，CANN能够帮助开发者识别出哪些操作或环节拖慢了模型执行速度。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111100759-ccwytgh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111100759-ccwytgh","updated":"20241111100810"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111100759-y1zklso","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111100759-y1zklso","updated":"20241111100759"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**调试工具**：CANN还提供了调试工具，开发者可以跟踪模型的执行过程，查看每个操作的执行状态，进行故障排除和调优。"}]},{"ID":"20241111100810-x2lhm94","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20241111100810-x2lhm94","updated":"20241111100810"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"CANN使用流程"}]},{"ID":"20241111100810-5erthug","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20241111100810-5erthug","updated":"20241111100810"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111100810-fhwuewa","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20241111100810-fhwuewa","updated":"20241111100810"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111100810-cw5bhsa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111100810-cw5bhsa","updated":"20241111100810"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**模型训练**：使用TensorFlow、PyTorch等框架进行模型训练，获得模型权重和计算图。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111100810-a821onc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20241111100810-a821onc","updated":"20241111100810"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111100810-gmi216a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111100810-gmi216a","updated":"20241111100810"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**模型转换**：使用CANN的 **Model Zoo** 或相关工具将训练好的模型转换为Ascend NPU支持的格式（如AICore格式）。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111100810-ksci673","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20241111100810-ksci673","updated":"20241111100810"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111100810-7gi7yf4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111100810-7gi7yf4","updated":"20241111100810"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**优化**："}]},{"ID":"20241111100810-e93f4wi","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111100810-e93f4wi","updated":"20241111100810"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111100810-q560jkn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111100810-q560jkn","updated":"20241111100810"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111100810-j3eblsj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111100810-j3eblsj","updated":"20241111100810"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"使用CANN对模型进行量化、剪枝和计算图优化。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111100810-ity1jle","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111100810-ity1jle","updated":"20241111100810"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111100810-qjd77tc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111100810-qjd77tc","updated":"20241111100810"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"调整模型以适配Ascend硬件，确保资源最优利用。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241111100810-nr1v2s1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20241111100810-nr1v2s1","updated":"20241111100810"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111100810-f9ley37","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111100810-f9ley37","updated":"20241111100810"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**编译与部署**：使用CANN进行模型编译，生成适合在Ascend硬件上运行的二进制文件，然后部署到实际的硬件平台上。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111100810-ccldoqv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NS4=","Num":5},"Properties":{"id":"20241111100810-ccldoqv","updated":"20241111100810"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111100810-gveynwh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111100810-gveynwh","updated":"20241111100810"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**性能调优**：在推理过程中，使用CANN的性能分析工具来检测瓶颈，并进行相应的优化。"}]}]}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101535-6wuplwn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101535-6wuplwn","updated":"20241111101535"}},{"ID":"20241111101537-vjh6gy0","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20241111101537-vjh6gy0","updated":"20241111101630"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20241111101538-zdsxq85","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-zdsxq85","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**FLOPS（Floating Point Operations Per Second）** 和 **TOPS（Tera Operations Per Second）** 都是衡量计算设备（如NPU、GPU、CPU等）性能的指标，但它们有一些重要的区别，主要体现在它们表示的计算类型和单位上。"}]},{"ID":"20241111101538-od3op95","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-od3op95","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1. **FLOPS（浮点运算每秒）**"}]},{"ID":"20241111101538-moppied","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-moppied","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-6os4gsf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-6os4gsf","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-bh0sp0d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-bh0sp0d","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**定义**：FLOPS表示每秒能够执行的浮点运算的数量。浮点运算主要包括加法、减法、乘法、除法等数学运算，通常用于需要高精度计算的任务（如科学计算、深度学习等）。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101538-xjwf0dq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-xjwf0dq","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-hc72wln","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-hc72wln","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**单位**："}]},{"ID":"20241111101538-o3o7fp9","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-o3o7fp9","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-q9ngb0a","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-q9ngb0a","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-m4yt07x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-m4yt07x","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**GFLOPS**：每秒十亿次浮点运算（Giga FLOPS）"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101538-qof4f1w","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-qof4f1w","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-e3hw7jh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-e3hw7jh","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**TFLOPS**：每秒万亿次浮点运算（Tera FLOPS）"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101538-s0q48mi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-s0q48mi","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-vpzyenm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-vpzyenm","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**PFLOPS**：每秒千万亿次浮点运算（Peta FLOPS）"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101538-ldfc2o2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-ldfc2o2","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-ed039dh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-ed039dh","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**作用**：FLOPS主要用于衡量设备的浮点计算能力，通常适用于那些涉及复杂计算、科学计算、图像处理和深度学习训练中的浮点计算的任务。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101538-rgbz3h9","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-rgbz3h9","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2. **TOPS（Tera Operations Per Second）**"}]},{"ID":"20241111101538-bh89czr","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-bh89czr","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-5sv2nm6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-5sv2nm6","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-qh3f2tz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-qh3f2tz","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**定义**：TOPS表示每秒能够执行的操作数，通常指的是一秒钟内可以执行多少次“操作”。这个“操作”不仅限于浮点计算，还包括整数运算、向量计算和其他类型的算术计算。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101538-vzle90q","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-vzle90q","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-qmmgjv4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-qmmgjv4","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**单位**："}]},{"ID":"20241111101538-71r8c0v","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-71r8c0v","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-m2igtat","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-m2igtat","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-t8uiqf7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-t8uiqf7","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**TOPS**：每秒万亿次操作（Tera Operations Per Second）"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101538-7lo6n0u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-7lo6n0u","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-6h7leau","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-6h7leau","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**作用**：TOPS通常用于衡量 **AI加速器**（如NPU、TPU、AI处理单元等）的计算性能，因为这些加速器通常会执行大量的整数运算（例如8-bit、16-bit整数运算），这些运算在神经网络推理中非常常见，特别是在量化后的深度学习模型中。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101538-rxq1p57","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-rxq1p57","updated":"20241111101630"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3. **FLOPS和TOPS的区别**"}]},{"ID":"20241111101538-t0piufz","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-t0piufz","updated":"20241111101630"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-np1khkq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-np1khkq","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-kvqqbro","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-kvqqbro","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**计算类型**："}]},{"ID":"20241111101538-1e5z6pd","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-1e5z6pd","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-ga86272","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-ga86272","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-0kruoyu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-0kruoyu","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**FLOPS**：专门衡量浮点运算的能力，适用于需要高精度的计算（如科学计算、浮点数运算密集型任务）。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101538-mss7r1x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-mss7r1x","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-w3ala4u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-w3ala4u","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**TOPS**：衡量所有类型的运算能力，特别是**整数运算**，适用于机器学习和AI加速，尤其是在深度学习推理时，使用低精度整数（如INT8、INT16）进行计算时，NPU通常会以TOPS来衡量。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101538-6amq7r6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-6amq7r6","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-4yz213p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-4yz213p","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**精度差异**："}]},{"ID":"20241111101538-b8s0vod","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-b8s0vod","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-6v0fy69","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-6v0fy69","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-geej5s7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-geej5s7","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**FLOPS**：通常针对**浮点数运算**，更精确，但计算量大。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101538-u8kwqdj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-u8kwqdj","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-jiu1nec","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-jiu1nec","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**TOPS**：通常涉及低精度（例如INT8、INT16等）整数运算，这使得它在AI推理中更加高效，尤其是在采用量化模型时，低精度计算能带来更高的吞吐量。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101538-dt19kvh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-dt19kvh","updated":"20241111101630"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-vvkt6ea","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-vvkt6ea","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**应用场景**："}]},{"ID":"20241111101538-ax1dbil","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-ax1dbil","updated":"20241111101630"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-mtx0twr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-mtx0twr","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-3bhfv5z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-3bhfv5z","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**FLOPS**：主要用于描述CPU、GPU等硬件在复杂的数学计算、图形渲染和其他浮点计算密集型任务中的表现。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101538-hq7s9ul","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-hq7s9ul","updated":"20241111101630"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101538-j6phdmc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101538-j6phdmc","updated":"20241111101538"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**TOPS**：主要用于描述AI加速器（尤其是NPU）在处理神经网络推理时的性能，尤其是在采用量化模型（低精度计算）时。"}]},{"ID":"20241111101630-5kypn6h","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20241111101630-5kypn6h","updated":"20241111101630"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"总结"}]},{"ID":"20241111101630-mxms981","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101630-mxms981","updated":"20241111101630"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101630-v307q9f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101630-v307q9f","updated":"20241111101630"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101630-r91nm87","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101630-r91nm87","updated":"20241111101630"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**FLOPS** 主要衡量浮点运算的能力，通常用于高精度计算任务。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101630-3l3o4ra","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101630-3l3o4ra","updated":"20241111101630"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101630-ltunmkx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101630-ltunmkx","updated":"20241111101630"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**TOPS** 衡量所有类型的操作能力，尤其适用于机器学习和AI推理任务，特别是低精度计算（如INT8）时，因此NPU更倾向于使用TOPS作为性能指标。"}]}]}]}]}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101842-iygqvyg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101842-iygqvyg","updated":"20241111101842"}},{"ID":"20241111101842-umbaqoz","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20241111101842-umbaqoz","updated":"20241111101856"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20241111101843-zl2qwtf","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20241111101843-zl2qwtf","updated":"20241111101843"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1. **NPU的设计更专注于AI任务**"}]},{"ID":"20241111101843-zap8qie","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101843-zap8qie","updated":"20241111101843"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101843-fg0i4wx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101843-fg0i4wx","updated":"20241111101843"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101843-d2o7kjv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101843-d2o7kjv","updated":"20241111101843"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**NPU** 是专门为 **神经网络推理**（尤其是深度学习）优化的硬件。它采用了针对性强的硬件架构，能够高效地处理 **矩阵乘法**、**卷积运算** 等深度学习模型中频繁出现的操作。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101843-bmbbwvc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101843-bmbbwvc","updated":"20241111101843"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101843-bifft6e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101843-bifft6e","updated":"20241111101843"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"NPU在设计上通常优化了 **低精度整数运算**（如INT8、INT16），这些运算在深度学习推理（尤其是量化模型）中非常常见，并能提高吞吐量和计算效率。比如，许多NPU支持 **8-bit**（INT8）计算，这对于深度学习模型推理来说通常已经足够，并且大大节省了计算和内存资源。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101843-xmlsn3s","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20241111101843-xmlsn3s","updated":"20241111101843"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2. **能效优化**"}]},{"ID":"20241111101843-nezxjsd","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101843-nezxjsd","updated":"20241111101843"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101843-em97w9y","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101843-em97w9y","updated":"20241111101843"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101843-zqhhpjr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101843-zqhhpjr","updated":"20241111101843"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**NPU** 通常具有 **更低的功耗**，这使得它们在 **边缘计算**、**嵌入式设备** 或 **移动设备**（如智能手机、智能摄像头、自动驾驶系统等）中更加适用。由于NPU针对AI计算进行硬件级优化，相比于GPU，它能够以更低的功耗执行相同或类似的任务。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101843-fcdkrfu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101843-fcdkrfu","updated":"20241111101843"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101843-1ueriwv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101843-1ueriwv","updated":"20241111101843"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"相反，GPU是为 **图形渲染** 和通用计算设计的，虽然它们也支持深度学习，但功耗较高，并且通常不如NPU在推理任务上高效。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101843-3zp16r0","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20241111101843-3zp16r0","updated":"20241111101843"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3. **高效的推理性能**"}]},{"ID":"20241111101843-cbv43n0","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101843-cbv43n0","updated":"20241111101843"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101843-ss6n757","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101843-ss6n757","updated":"20241111101843"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101843-u0jj7bw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101843-u0jj7bw","updated":"20241111101843"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**NPU** 通过 **专用硬件加速**，使得神经网络推理过程中的一些常见操作（例如卷积运算、矩阵乘法、激活函数计算等）可以以 **更高的吞吐量** 和 **更低的延迟** 来完成。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101843-fb7yk21","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101843-fb7yk21","updated":"20241111101843"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101843-f8qb2bl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101843-f8qb2bl","updated":"20241111101843"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这种专用加速使得NPU在处理深度学习推理时相比通用的GPU能够提供更 **高效的性能**，尤其是在对 **计算速度** 和 **延迟** 有严格要求的场景下。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101843-x4a5p0k","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20241111101843-x4a5p0k","updated":"20241111101856"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4. **AI芯片的目标是推理而非训练**"}]},{"ID":"20241111101843-ne2qoe7","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101843-ne2qoe7","updated":"20241111101856"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101843-bcbd8us","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101843-bcbd8us","updated":"20241111101843"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101843-k53uaox","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101843-k53uaox","updated":"20241111101843"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"传统的 **GPU** 最初是为 **图形渲染** 和 **并行计算** 设计的，虽然它在 **深度学习训练** 中表现优秀，但在 **推理**（尤其是边缘设备上的推理）中，NPU通常提供了更为专业的优化。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101843-d5yfsq1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101843-d5yfsq1","updated":"20241111101843"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101843-q3m0vzb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101843-q3m0vzb","updated":"20241111101843"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对于深度学习的 **训练** 阶段，GPU仍然占据主导地位，因为训练过程通常需要更高的浮点计算性能和大规模并行计算。而对于 **推理** 阶段（即使用训练好的模型进行预测），NPU则能提供更高的 **推理吞吐量** 和 **较低的延迟**，并且在能效上表现优越。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101856-4e62hdk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101856-4e62hdk","updated":"20241111101856"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101856-6eeprkb","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20241111101856-6eeprkb","updated":"20241111101856"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**AI芯片的应用场景**"}]},{"ID":"20241111101856-eluzifn","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101856-eluzifn","updated":"20241111101856"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101856-78pmnh0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101856-78pmnh0","updated":"20241111101856"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101856-ann31a3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101856-ann31a3","updated":"20241111101856"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**NPU** 通常用于深度学习的 **推理任务**，比如图像分类、目标检测、语音识别、自然语言处理等，它们广泛应用于 **智能家居设备**、**智能交通**、**自动驾驶**、**边缘计算设备** 等场景。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241111101856-0u46l95","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241111101856-0u46l95","updated":"20241111101856"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241111101856-d1lxofr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241111101856-d1lxofr","updated":"20241111101856"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**GPU** 更多地用于需要 **高精度计算** 和 **大规模数据并行计算** 的任务，例如 **深度学习训练**、**图形渲染** 和 **科学计算** 等。"}]}]}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250211091254-10ntr2w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250211091254-10ntr2w","updated":"20250211091254"}},{"ID":"20250211091254-48tqup8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250211091254-48tqup8","updated":"20250211091254"}},{"ID":"20250211084516-l2gdtc4","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20250211084516-l2gdtc4","updated":"20250211084542"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"目标检测和图像分类的区别"}]},{"ID":"20250211084619-evr73fa","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250211084619-evr73fa","updated":"20250211084654"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"图像分类"}]},{"ID":"20250211084640-0dpgi54","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20250211084640-0dpgi54","updated":"20250211084647"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250211084647-0qgi1hd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250211084647-0qgi1hd","updated":"20250211084647"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"图像分类的任务是对整张图像进行归类，判断该图像主要属于哪一类。例如，给定一张图像，模型输出“猫”、“狗”、“汽车”等类别标签。这里的输出是对整个图像的整体判断，通常只有一个主要的类别标签（或多个标签，但不涉及位置信息）。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250211084619-w5iwcrq","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250211084619-w5iwcrq","updated":"20250211091333"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"目标检测"}]},{"ID":"20250211084654-jl17uku","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20250211084654-jl17uku","updated":"20250211084702"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250211084702-4goizy8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250211084702-4goizy8","updated":"20250211084702"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"目标检测不仅需要判断图像中包含哪些对象，还需要准确定位出这些对象在图像中的位置。输出结果通常包含多个目标的类别标签以及它们对应的边界框（bounding box），即在图像中的具体位置。例如，在一张街景图像中，目标检测模型可以标出“行人”、“车辆”、“交通信号灯”等对象，并用矩形框标记出它们的位置。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250211084704-mdmye0k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250211084704-mdmye0k","updated":"20250211084704"}},{"ID":"20250211091303-bryudhd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250211091303-bryudhd","updated":"20250211091303"}},{"ID":"20250211091303-37s0dbe","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20250211091303-37s0dbe","updated":"20250211091410"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"回归问题和分类问题的区别"}]},{"ID":"20250211091335-wpj5o0g","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20250211091335-wpj5o0g","updated":"20250211091357"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250211091342-hcez030","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20250211091342-hcez030","updated":"20250211091406"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"回归问题 (Regression)"}]},{"ID":"20250211091342-ysef240","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250211091342-ysef240","updated":"20250211091342"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250211091342-mu1m04w","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250211091342-mu1m04w","updated":"20250211091342"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250211091342-fe30tpl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250211091342-fe30tpl","updated":"20250211091342"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"预测**连续型数值**（continuous value），取值范围无限或多个可能的实数值。\n**典型任务**：预测年龄、股价走向、降水量等。\n**数学模型特性**：因变量（target variable）“Y” ∈ ℝ。"}]}]}]},{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250211091342-sc91ekx","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20250211091342-sc91ekx","updated":"20250211091357"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"分类问题 (Classification)"}]},{"ID":"20250211091342-rhcqnbm","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250211091342-rhcqnbm","updated":"20250211091406"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250211091342-e13dcam","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250211091342-e13dcam","updated":"20250211091342"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250211091342-kxrrr4s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250211091342-kxrrr4s","updated":"20250211091342"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"预测**离散类别标签**（discrete label），取值有限（少数特定类别）。\n**典型任务**：垃圾分类、垃圾邮件识别、图像分类（狗？猫？车？人？）。\n**数学模型特性**：设定预测类别，例如 {0, 1}（二分类），或 {Red, Green, Blue}（多类分布）。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250211091410-0ye4m7f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250211091410-0ye4m7f","updated":"20250211091410"}}]}